data.description: Incredible chance to acquire a spacious 4,000+ square foot residence situated directly opposite Prairie Vista Golf Course. This exclusive property boasts a nearly one-acre lot, nestled amongst other luxurious homes on generous lots. The current owner offers an assumable loan with a remarkable 2.675% rate through Penny Mac. This 5-bedroom home is ideal for large families and features a finished basement, complete with an extra family room, perfect for hosting gatherings. Enjoy the benefits of a tankless water heater and a dual-zone HVAC system. Don't miss out on the opportunity to explore this remarkable home today!
